reviewText: Purchased these DVD's for my Mother and she is enjoying watching them.  Hallmark always makes movies with morals and values to the stories, that is why my Mother likes that type of program.

reviewText: This set was as described. Hallmark always has movies that the whole family can watch without being afraid that it might not be appropriate for children. I don't have children to watch, but I don't like filthy language and a lot of other stuff in the new movies either.
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)

reviewText: These sets are awesome.  Hallmark has many wonderful movies and are good for viewing at any time.  I love to have them on hand for days when I just need a little "something".
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)

reviewText: These movies were really good. All of them. Not for all ages. they are entertaining and more adult themed.The war one was really good. showed a peace during times of stress. All the acting is surperbly done.I will watch them every year at holiday time.
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)

reviewText: I keep forgetting that Hallmark is not as restricted as formerly.  These topics deal with war (a well-made video but not for kids), some far out philosophies and abnormal relationships.  Not for folks who are attempting to instill wholesome values in their kids.
summary: not your family values type of collection
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)

reviewText: I enjoyed every movie.  They were wonderful.  They were all different but everyone was intriguing and I would really recommend them. I was home ill and watched all four one day.
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)

reviewText: Just good movies of general interest and to pass the time. Nothing outstanding but then nothing objectionable either from where I sit.
Title: Hallmark Collector's Set: Volume 3 Silent Night / In His Father's Shoes / Out of the Woods / Where There's A Will)
